 Nollywood actor Gideon Okeke has announced that he is expecting his Second child with his wife, Chidera. This makes it Gideon’s third child and his second with Chidera, expected to arrive in July. The movie star made this known via his Instagram page on Thursday, April 8, 2021, where he shared a video of his wife, Dera’s ultrasound scan. He captioned the photo “OBUMNEME? Naa! God is good to Me. Steady beating My daddy’s achievements on all fronts. On my 3rd Seed. Believe it Oh! Family: Because 2 people fell in love. Big Win o! BUN IN THE O. ??,” View this post on Instagram A post shared by Gideon Okeke (@gideonokeke.ng)